Version 0.8.0
---------------------
Flow object now implements "reduce" method with implementation similar to Array.reduce
New operators:
    - skipWhile - Skips elements until predicate returns a falsey value
    - takeWhile - Yields elements until predicate returns a falsey value

Version 0.7.1
---------------------
Updated vulnerable dependencies


Version 0.7.0
---------------------
Flow object now implements iterator protocol. Can now be used in for...of loops or Array.from
Fixed Linting issues
